deck: Ruby Rekjavik was an escaped experiment who has the ability to make the transition from adult to teen to pre-pubescent, with each stage having a different set of powers. Ruby has the powers of Cryo-kinesis: (Ice powers)
description: Ruby Rekjavik was a genetic experiment by an alien scientist in trying to create an one person army (the theory was to have the individual multiply by cloning itself.) Ruby was considered a failure, as she was only able to change into two other versions of herself. The alien was so mentally devastated that he committed suicide, leaving her to fend for herself. It wasn't until Golden Retrievals was tasked with repossessing the lab and all contents that Ruby was discovered and using her abilities and different personae, she was able to defend the lab. It wasn't until they sent their top agent (Gunther Smythe) that he was able to talk her down and even persuaded her to use her abilities to earn a purpose and a living. Ruby has the ability to create ice, being a cryo-kenetic. Her second personality is that of a 16 year old teen, known as Catnip Annie: who in turn, is an Empath who can read and/or transmit emotions to any sentient being. Lastly is Kitten Atomik, an 9 year old version that is a super powered being with the naivety of a young girl. Each one of these versions prove a valuable asset in the business of Galactic repossessions, process serving, escorting and bodyguarding., Ruby can be a one woman team, but prefers to work with her husband and learn the ropes, as well as the ways of the universe.
name: Ruby Rekjavik

deck: Special agent of 'Golden Retrievals' a compamy that sanctions repossessions, salvage missions, and process serving throughout the galaxy. Along with his partner/wife Ruby Rekjavik, Gunther take on the impossible tasks of repo work. A former member of the Gun-Wolves, (specially designed astro-soldiers) Gunther can transform his arms into various firearms, ranging from pistols to high caliber cannons depending on the situation.
name: Gunther Smythe

description:
Origin

Very little is known about Hands. At some point he descended into the subway system, where he became a member of the Dead Dogs, one of the subway pirate crews that haunt the tunnels below New York. He was taken on by No-Beard as his personal assistant.

Creation

Hands was created by Grant Morrison and Cameron Stewart. He made his first appearance in Seven Soldiers: Guardian #2

Major Story Arcs

Seven Soldiers of Victory

Working for No-Beard, Hands holds the map of the secret subway tunnels for No-Beard to steer by, and later rigs the wheel so the President Clinton will be able to steer while the pirates launch an attack on the Sun Lubbers. He is thrown from the train when it crashes, and dies in No-Beard's arms after telling him that he was not as good a pirate as All-Beard.

Powers and Abilities

Hands has no known superhuman powers or abilities. He possesses two functional hands, for which he was prized by No-Beard.
name: Hands

description:
Maiden America was first introduced in a two-part short story in a one shot magazine called 'Gritz-N-Gravy' in 2001. Later revised in Action Bunny Comix #2.

Siobahn O'Banyon lived in a fractured America. In the year 205X, the various foreign nations paid politicians and bought portions of America, causing the division of the country. Self-sufficient city-states were re-established, while the Arab states established Sharia laws, Other nations brought their ideologies to the land, creating chaos and fear.

The Daughter of an Irish brew master, a young Siobahn O'Banyon had entered a tween talent contest, which was a cleverly disguised sex slave ring. Her feisty attitude eventually had her sold to an outpost scientist, where she stumbled upon his discovery of a new energy source (Promaethion-5). The unstable energies destroyed the lab, but Siobahn miraculously survived and quickly exhibited strange powers. She soon joined a traveling caravan/circus and secretly began her mission to free victims of the slave trade. Her exploits were noticed by a secret group of freedom fighters, funded by 'Old Money'. Intrigued by their proposition, Siobahn agreed to become a symbol to unite the fractured country, and in using her powers, fight against those who would keep America divided and chaotic. Backed by a growing army called The Sons Of Liberty, Siobahn O'Banyon became Maiden Amerika.
name: Maiden Amerika

description: Unable to control her growth spurts, the United States Government tried to keep Becca under close scrutiny, but the Über-Sapien known as Zeron spirited her away and changed her game. With his otherworldly powers, Zeron drew out the alien energies from her bloodstream, compressed and concentrated them and allowed her the ability to control her size and create a natural armor form her body. The armor acts like an exoskeleton, giving her increased strength, 10x more than she has as a giantess. Becca prefers to fight in the nude, practicing her fighting techniques on unwitting monsters, but when the situations become to dire or if the stakes are too high, she armors up and meets the challenge with the utmost seriousness.
name: Becca Starr

description:
Born in 31 BC, Nefertari was the Priestess/Queen in Kemet (The REAL Name before the Romans renamed it Egypt) and when the Roman Empire made another push into the fertile crescent, they were repelled by the Sword of Pharaohs (a male at that time). A Roman commander by the name of Lionus Octavious was sent as ambassador, but in actuality a spy, who seduced Nefertari to learn the secret of the Sword and killed him. As Nefertari's people were killed or enslaved, the Goddess Ma'At punished her by turning her into an immortal *Tyrean Sphinx to wander the Earth and mourn her people. She was also given the job to safeguard the sacred relics of the Gods and train the new Sword when necessary.

*Tyrean is Purple. The color was taken from the dye from a particular clam and was called Tyrean Purple, but was shortened to just Purple.
name: Nefertari Hormakhet
